        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/n/8c91f0/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2020-02-28T00:50:24.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"8\" data-topic=\"158753\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Coche made great 2001\u2019s , the best in white Burgundy imho , but now they are on their decline.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>???</p>\n<p>How can they be the best whites if they didn\u2019t even make it to the two decade mark?</p>\n<p>Or do you simply dislike the vintage as a whole?</p>",
